P2-P4 (Fig. 5
B-D
). Intercoxal sclerite unornamented. Coxa and basis with complex spinular ornamentation as figured. Exopod 3-segmented. Endopod 2-segmented. Endopodal and exopodal segments with spinular rows along inner and outer margins. Exp-1 of P2-P3 without spinules along inner margin. Enp-1 of P2 without inner seta. Terminal outer seta of P2 enp-2 bare. P4 exp-2 with one plumose inner seta. With a pore on anterior surface of enp-2 and anterior surface of exp-2 and -3. Exp-1 and -2 (and -3 in P4) with a posterior spinule patches. Enp-2 with a posterior spinular row subdistally.
